      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BACON (1) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (18.26) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Key player on best and expected to bounce back. KINGSBRAE MAGGIE (7) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 0.8 lengths winner (17.68) over 300m at this track. Can make it two on the bounce. STANLEY RUPERT (2) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths (17.59) behind Imogene Pass at this track. The form out of last race has been strong. Well-placed to take this out. ELLA BLACK (5) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
